        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7603",
        "content": "Still I consoled myself with the reflection that the tide of ill luck would not run against me forever, and so determined to make a bold push for information at the rout of that bewitching little angel, the graceful mrs Pirouette.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
