        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7603",
        "content": "I say\"--[here mr s thought proper to put his finger to the side of his nose]--\"I say, you don't mean to insinuate now, really and truly, and conscientiously, that you don't know all about that affair of Smith's, as well as I do, eh?",
