        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7603",
        "content": "It was early when I called, and the General was dressing; but I pleaded urgent business, and was shown at once into his bed room by an old negro valet, who remained in attendance during my visit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
