        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7603",
        "content": "\"Strange you shouldn't know me though, isn't it?\" presently re squeaked the nondescript, which I now perceived was performing, upon the floor, some inexplicable evolution, very analogous to the drawing on of a stocking.",
